    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Bottles of a distinctive shape, used to hold champagne or other sparkling wines. These have deep punts that prevent the bottle from shattering during the second fermentation of the contents. </Note_Text>
